2.00	Minor_characters_in_The_Hitchhiker's_Guide_to_the_Galaxy	List of minor The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy characters	The following is an alphabetical list of the minor characters in the various versions of The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy, by Douglas Adams. The descriptions of the characters are accompanied by information on details about appearances and references to the characters. Major characters—Arthur Dent, Ford Prefect, Zaphod Beeblebrox, Marvin the Paranoid Android, Trillian, and Slartibartfast—are separately described.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d8/God_%28Non-Existance_of%29.jpg/200px-God_%28Non-Existance_of%29.jpg
